o a service you define, and your team can confirm, reschedule, or cancel as needed."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients reschedule or cancel appointments online?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can manage their appointments directly through the portal or mobile app. Clinics stay in control, with the option to confirm rescheduling requests. If the clinic needs to reschedule an appointment, patients can confirm it from their end."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What happens when a patient cancels a paid appointment?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When a cancellation occurs, the payment is refunded as credits into the patient's wallet within the system. Patients can use these credits for future bookings, while providers avoid payment gateway refund hassles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can appointments be linked to services and multiple clinic locations?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Appointments are mapped to the services you offer—such as in-person and telehealth consultations—and can be tied to the correct provider and location across multi-branch clinics."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients manage their appointments from a portal or mobile app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patients can log into their secure account online or via the mobile app to book, reschedule, cancel, and view their appointment history at any time. They can also confirm any rescheduling initiated by the clinic."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do automated reminders reduce no-shows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The system sends patients timely confirmations and reminders by email, SMS, or in-app notifications. Providers also receive daily digests of upcoming appointments. This helps reduce no-shows and keeps schedules on track."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does appointment scheduling connect with consultation documentation and records?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Once an appointment is completed, providers can generate consultation notes, prescriptions, lab orders, and visit summaries. Patients receive secure access to the records that are meant for them."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can we customize booking rules and availability?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Clinics can set their own availability, define booking windows, configure auto-cancellations for unpaid appointments, and choose how appointments are managed with configurable settings."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the appointment scheduling system HIPAA compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The system is HIPAA-compliant and designed to protect patient data while supporting secure communications, payments, and record-keeping. None of the appointment related notifications contain PHI. Patients have securely log in to their account to view details."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly can we implement appointment scheduling, and what support is available?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most clinics can get started within a day, as all you need to get started is to configure all your services and provider schedules. To accept payments from your patients, you will also need to add in your payment processor account so that payments directly reach your own bank account. Comprehensive help is available."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="How does online appointment scheduling work?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">How does online appointment s